DataElement.preferredName: Circulating Tumor Cell Specimen Preservation Agent Lot Identifier Number
DataElement.preferredDefinition: the unique identifier assigned to a lot or batch of a circulating tumor cell preservation agent, a chemical preservative to prevent the decay or degradation of metastatic cancer cells found in a specimen of peripheral blood.
